# FORK-CUSTOM: Intentionally-empty builtin-skills corpus.
#
# This fork does not embed any builtin skills into the binary. The
# `include_dir!` macro in `aionui-extension/src/skill_service.rs` points here
# instead of `../aionui-app/assets/builtin-skills`, so the embedded corpus is
# empty and no skills are auto-injected. All skills are installed on demand from
# the Skill Market.
#
# The upstream `builtin-skills/` directory is left untouched so future rebases
# against upstream stay conflict-free.
